{
  "stem": "3360.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "For English, we had another teacher, for French we-- no, I started with English.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So French didn't come until later.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "For English, we had another teacher.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "For history, we had another teacher.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "For Geometry, we had another teacher.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But this was our so-called homeroom teacher, Miss.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Arnold.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Fraulein Arnold.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so she would start the class.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was-- of course, you said, how did we know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Or, how-- how, you know, things were done?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, you either knew it by-- you knew it by instinct.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Or, you knew enough to know what was going on and what the attempts were and what the goals were of the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the class was starting.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there had been notices made whether the few remaining Jewish pupils in that school would remain in class while this instruction was taking place.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the first few times, I was there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I couldn't leave.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, I would have been-- I would have been punished if I had left on my own.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I-- no decision had been made that I should not be there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So she started to talk about this and that and the glory of Germany and how Hitler was going to, you know, restore everything to its glory and to the German people, and then a whole bunch of stuff.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then, of course, you had to-- you had to start on the Jews to infuse the children-- and we were then 10 years old, 10 to 10 and 1/2-- to infuse them with this un-- unlimited hatred by making Jews appear as such outrageously ugly and evil bogeymen.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So she was-- they were talking about the racial characteristics, blonde hair, blue eyes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, Jews are dark and this and that and the other thing.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
